data.title: Warner Recorded Music
data.meta_description: Led by an independent spirit and a devotion to great music, our renowned collection of distinctive record labels is home to the world’s most popular and influential artists.
data.text:
Every label within Warner Recorded Music has its own story, history, and culture. What unites us above all is our commitment to powering original voices. With over 70 years of shared knowledge and a future-forward independent spirit, we’re obsessed with turning dreams into careers.

Whatever stage an artist is at in their career, our distribution & DIY offerings give flexible ways to release music independently, while staying plugged into Warner Music globally.
